history.content:
I am trying to pursue robotics in software/ML aspect, and I am having hard time choosing which upper div class to put a priority on. I am a transfer and I got 4 more semesters from 2020 Spring!
106A 106B
120 123 128
126 127 189
162
  1. If I had to drop two classes from above, which ones should I drop?
  2. I am not so sure if I should take 123 for the role I am interested in. Would it worth to take it? I thought it would be necessary as it might have close relationship with robotic perceptions.
  3. I know that 106A/B both covers some of robotic control. So I was wondering if those would be significant enough that 128 would be redundant, or make 128 not worth to take.
  4. I wonder how 162 would positively affect my future career path. I only know that it's a must class for anyone who is doing CS, but I don't know anything specific related to my career goal.
Thank you!
history.subject: Priority on upper div class for robotics
